{"tid":370825,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★美軍阿帕契直升機安裝雷射炮　成功射中目標","createTime":"2017-08-23T09:05:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-23T15:06:41.000Z","uid":19454,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7ee05d681e7d2bd020955fe5a17490dae3bcb97f","tid":370825,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T09:05:11.000Z","msg":"在科幻電影中時常看到戰機利用雷射炮摧毀敵機。但這種場面似乎在現實上能夠實現。美國陸軍已成功在阿帕契直升機上，安裝高能雷射炮，並實際進行射擊測試。射擊測試完全成功，成功命中靜止的無人目標，射程達到1.4公里。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/high_energy_laser_lead_img-694x463.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F08%2Fhigh_energy_laser_lead_img-694x463.jpg&h=69140fa0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n早前美國海軍派駐波斯灣的兩棲運輸艦龐塞號（USS Ponce）裝上雷射炮之後，陸軍亦不讓海軍專美。負責這次雷射炮安裝的是美國雷神公司（Raytheon），他們與美國陸軍阿帕契計劃管理辦公室、美國特種司令部合作，在陸軍的Ah-64阿帕契直升機機身上亦安裝了雷射炮。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/23/170344_812749e1a307f38fd0a88b54bea55ff2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F23%2F170344_812749e1a307f38fd0a88b54bea55ff2.png&h=d97470d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n裝上雷射炮的阿帕契直升機，在新墨西哥州的白沙飛彈靶場中作射擊測試，結果雷射炮成功擊中在1.4公里以外的無人目標。這是第一次在旋轉扇葉的直升機上，以各種飛行姿態、高速之下成功命中目標，直升機上使用雷射攻擊變成可能。不過日後要在更高速的噴射戰機上使用，就需要更高的技術。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/23/170437_9ef5055324e69f335d69b27ea40d2202.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F23%2F170437_9ef5055324e69f335d69b27ea40d2202.png&h=b6c2f40b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雷射炮的優點是，攻擊時無聲無色，很難被敵人以肉眼確認，另一方面由於雷射炮行走速度高，命中率可大幅提升，而且與一般導彈相比，成本將會更低，還可一次過攻擊多個目標。不過在聯合國裁軍事務廳的《特定常規武器公約》中，禁止對人類直接使用雷射武器，似乎在進行攻擊時，司令需要有更多考量。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2017/08/23/lasergun/fun-tech/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2017%2F08%2F23%2Flasergun%2Ffun-tech%2F&d=dMw%2FSDUuvxnscJWfGjG4dzANphTrK3OAdhrcB0lChBw%3D&h=b56d30b2\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2017/08/23/lasergun/fun-tech/</a>"},{"pid":"28e29e532e8e3f5fd8f19a9d6d49c8d838f5aa8b","tid":370825,"uid":90,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T09:07:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de8b94ac0ba733340dfe6141edf35221e0cfd975","tid":370825,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T09:09:06.000Z","msg":"要來了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1f5fba378d1bc2cd4420fbb7d4c02b381a718e2","tid":370825,"uid":63669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T09:09:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9e5a626bf68e4e6dd89b3e434a656c5a0ffe5ba","tid":370825,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T09:09:56.000Z","msg":"我地中國人飛機大炮更強"},{"pid":"02ede5ec9afa3b43012ab957612424a9c7a67e43","tid":370825,"uid":90,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T09:10:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我地中國人飛機大炮更強</blockquote><br />\n樓豬一個頂十個美軍"},{"pid":"846fec54b19a514fd489aacd0292711ab0371e2f","tid":370825,"uid":55597,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T09:11:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://cnc-redalert.ru/wp-content/gallery/ren2_scr1/gallery_3_69_48974.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcnc-redalert.ru%2Fwp-content%2Fgallery%2Fren2_scr1%2Fgallery_3_69_48974.jpg&h=18fb0011&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"00c4704c30adba5951eb2bddf77dca14af5d078d","tid":370825,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T09:11:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我地中國人飛機大炮更強</blockquote><br />